videos.description: Zion Williamson drives to the rack and is rejected by Brandon Clarke, who runs the floor and stuffs home a miss.
videos.headline: Clarke denies Zion, finishes putback

videos.description: Tre Jones fails on the wide-open dunk and Gonzaga pushes the miss to Brandon Clarke, who finishes the athletic reverse layup.
videos.headline: Jones whiffs on dunk, Gonzaga cashes in

videos.description: Geno Crandall slashes to the hoop and tosses up an off-balanced scoop shot over Cam Reddish for the and-1.
videos.headline: Gonzaga's Crandall finishes and-1 over Reddish

videos.description: Zach Norvell Jr. drives baseline past RJ Barrett and kisses glass on the reverse layup for Gonzaga.
videos.headline: Norvell Jr. blows by Barrett, scoops in ridiculous reverse

videos.description: Zion Williamson hustles back on defense to pin Brandon Clarke's fast-break layup off the backboard for a vicious block.
videos.headline: Zion channels LeBron on chasedown block

videos.description: Tre Jones closes the first half with a banked half-court shot to pull Duke within 8 of Gonzaga at intermission.
videos.headline: Jones cans half-courter at first-half buzzer

videos.description: Zion Williamson collects an offensive rebound, misses the wide-open dunk and Corey Kispert drains an open 3 for Gonzaga in transition.
videos.headline: Zion's missed uncontested dunk leads to Zags' 3

videos.description: Zion Williamson sends Zach Norvell Jr.'s layup off the backboard and Tre Jones scoops home a lefty lay-in on the other end.
videos.headline: Zion's block ignites crowd, Jones lay-in

videos.description: Zion Williamson swallows up Geno Crandall's shot attempt but Duke misses a transition 3, leading to Josh Perkins burying a long-distance trey for the Zags.
videos.headline: Zion smothers shot, sparks insane sequence

videos.description: RJ Barrett weaves through traffic and throws down the two-handed slam for Duke.
videos.headline: Barrett drops 2-handed hammer

videos.description: Zion Williamson collects the offensive rebound on RJ Barrett's miss and rises up for the two-handed hammer.
videos.headline: Zion throws down monstrous dunk off Barrett miss

videos.description: RJ Barrett drives to the rack with a full head of steam and slams the left-handed hammer on Gonzaga's Rui Hachimura.
videos.headline: Barrett obliterates Hachimura on fast-break slam

videos.description: Rui Hachimura's pair of missed free throws gives Duke an opportunity to tie the score, but RJ Barrett runs into a wall of defenders and is blocked on his attempt.
videos.headline: Barrett rejected on tying attempt in final seconds

videos.description: RJ Barrett and Zion Williamson combine for 45 points, but can't score in the final minute as No. 1 Duke falls to No. 3 Gonzaga 89-87.

tracking.trackingName: COM_NCB Highlight (Gonzaga holds off Duke to win Maui Invitational) 2018/11/21 ESHEET SOTFUll

videos.headline: Gonzaga holds off Duke to win Maui Invitational

videos.description: Gonzaga head coach Mark Few is elated his team pulled off the win against Duke as the game drew closer in the final minutes.

tracking.trackingName: COM_NCB Interview (Few: 'We were lucky enough to get the win') 2018/11/21

videos.headline: Few: 'We were lucky enough to get the win'
